#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:1
msgid "E0071"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `core_package_not_imported`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:5
msgid "Core package used without an explicit import."
msgstr "使用了未显式导入的 core 包。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:7
msgid ""
"MoonBit still recognizes some packages under `moonbitlang/core` when they"
" are referenced by their conventional aliases, but relying on that "
"implicit import is deprecated. Add the package to `moon.pkg` instead."
msgstr ""
"当代码通过约定俗成的别名引用 `moonbitlang/core` 下的某些包时，MoonBit 仍会识别它们，"
"但依赖这种隐式导入的写法已经被弃用。请改为在 `moon.pkg` 中添加对应的包。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:13
#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:25
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn make_buffer() -> @buffer.Buffer {\n"
"  @buffer.new()\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  ignore(make_buffer())\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:19
msgid "Declare the core package import in `moon.pkg`."
msgstr "在 `moon.pkg` 中声明 core 包导入。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0071.md:21
msgid ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/buffer\" @buffer,\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
